decoded sequence. The pre/post atom synthesis is the next
iteration's work (the "symbolic executor" piece); for the
demo, see the worked example in
`SVM/SBPF/Macros.lean` (`logger_macro_spec_auto`) where the
theorem is proved by `sl_block_auto` against the same
instruction sequence.
